# --- CUSTOM AURA SECURITY OVERRIDES ---

# 1. PROTECT SECRETS (Highest Priority)
.env
secrets.txt
config.json
api-keys.md
*.log

# 2. OFFLINE MOBILE DRAFTS
# Prevents phone junk from cluttering your professional repo.
*.tmp
*.bak
*~
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# 3. CUSTOM MEDIA
# If you store music stems or large video drafts, they stay local.
*.mp3
*.wav
*.mp4
